<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ح م م<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[١٤٧٥ - ح م م]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>حَمَّ٢ حَمَمْتُ، يَحُمّ، احْمُمْ/ حُمَّ، حَمًّا وحَمَمًا، فهو حامّ، والمفعول مَحْموم <span class="c2">(للمتعدِّي)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• حمَّ الشَّيءُ:</span> اسودَّ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• حمَّ الماءُ/ حمَّ الحديدُ:</span> سخُن.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">⦗٥٦٦⦘ • حمَّ التَّنُّورَ ونحوَه:</span> أوقَدَه.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">• حمَّ الماءَ ونحوَه:</span> سخَّنَه.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">• حمَّ اللهُ الأمرَ:</span> قضاه وقدّره.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>